snippet.title: Cryo Chamber
snippet.description:
Cryo Chamber is a Dark Ambient Music label run by Simon Heath (Atrium Carceri/Sabled Sun) focusing on dark atmospheric music with a cinematic edge. 

Come dream with the rest of the crew in Cryo Sleep as we hurtle through space in deep sleep. Choose an environment, close your eyes, and let your walls melt away to reveal ancient temples, dark cathedrals or post apocalyptic landscapes. 

❤Please support us at our bandcamp page if you like what we do❤ - https://cryochamber.bandcamp.com/

You are free to use our music for non-profit projects as long as you credit us properly and send us a message with a link to the project for approval, we are huge supporters of independent art. 

For licensing our music please contact us at our facebook page or our e-mail available from our bandcamp or domain.

Demo submission ( preferably streaming link / soundcloud) can be sent via a message to our facebook page
